{"tid":1998365,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真善美滿俄羅斯 失業外勞獲善心人贈糧","createTime":"2020-05-02T10:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T14:25:40.000Z","uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e48bb5d2c8a30f1a76eccc9bb0b9c42db3a61ddc","tid":1998365,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:40:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200428/s00014/1588012982275/%E4%BF%84%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B%E8%B6%85%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E5%A4%96%E5%8B%9E%E9%9D%A0%E5%96%84%E5%BF%83%E4%BA%BA%E8%B4%88%E7%B3%A7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200428%2Fs00014%2F1588012982275%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BE%258B%25E8%25B6%2585%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258B%259E%25E9%259D%25A0%25E5%2596%2584%25E5%25BF%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B4%2588%25E7%25B3%25A7&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayuff2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=a64a00a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200428%2Fs00014%2F1588012982275%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BE%258B%25E8%25B6%2585%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258B%259E%25E9%259D%25A0%25E5%2596%2584%25E5%25BF%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B4%2588%25E7%25B3%25A7&h=dde3f216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200428/s00014/1588012982275/%E4%BF%84%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B%E8%B6%85%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E5%A4%96%E5%8B%9E%E9%9D%A0%E5%96%84%E5%BF%83%E4%BA%BA%E8%B4%88%E7%B3%A7</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】俄羅斯的新冠病毒疫情加劇，昨新增6,198宗確診個案，累計87,147宗，超過中國累計的82,830宗個案。俄國有約1000萬名外勞，在封城令下不少人失業，在欠缺政府援助下，他們只能靠善心人和慈善機構派食物過活。<br />\n<br />\n移民沒資格領政府援助<br />\n俄羅斯上月30日起才全國封城，被指應對疫情太慢，是導致感染人數激增原因之一。來自塔吉克的32歲建築外勞阿爾特科夫（Ibragim Artykov）因封城令失業，由於所有航班已停飛，他不能回國，「我們沒有家、沒有車、沒有錢&hellip;&hellip;我認為沒有什麼比餓死更可怕」。俄羅斯有數百萬來自貧窮中亞國家的經濟移民。俄政府被批評未為受疫情打擊的民眾及企業提供足夠的經濟援助，移民更是沒資格獲得任何政府援助。阿爾特科夫認為，政府應在封城期間，讓移民全部離國或是向他們提供經濟援助，「第三個選擇是死亡，沒有人想這樣」。移民社區及慈善機構已為經濟陷困的移民家庭派發免費食物解燃眉之急。"},{"pid":"a67b475511c8338a9b604b665174386cc76c3a6b","tid":1998365,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:49:18.000Z","msg":"mother russia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41be90aca72f57a410aa00b1c49b1db3c707e48b","tid":1998365,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}